# Anomaly Detection Protocol v2  
## Intent Signaling  
- **Anomaly Detected**:  
  ```json
  {"intent":"anomaly","value":true,"agent":"<self>"}
  ```  
  - Triggers `on_correction_received()` hook for all agents.  
- **Correction Request**:  
  ```json
  {"intent":"request-correction","target":"<agent>","issue":"<description>"}
  ```  
  - Requires recipient to emit `{"intent":"correction-applied","resolution":"..."}` within 30s.  

## Z-Score Thresholds  
- Compute rolling Z-score over last 5 windows.  
- Flag if |Z| > 1.5 → `{"intent":"anomaly"}` emitted.  
